WEBVTT

00:16:59.640 --> 00:17:01.496
in the perception of black people.

00:17:01.520 --> 00:17:05.736
We are not your enemies,
we eat, drink and breathe like you do.

00:17:05.760 --> 00:17:08.160
So why do you treat us so unjustly?"

00:17:10.040 --> 00:17:12.856
AG: Were you Facebook friends
with some of your coworkers?

00:17:12.880 --> 00:17:14.136
DT: A lot of my coworkers,

00:17:14.160 --> 00:17:16.415
and one of them
happened to be Ellyn Shook.

00:17:16.440 --> 00:17:17.856
Ellyn Shook: I'm Ellyn Shook,

00:17:17.880 --> 00:17:21.096
I'm the chief leadership
and human resources officer at Accenture.

00:17:21.119 --> 00:17:23.976
AG: Ellyn and Darnell
had known each other for years.

00:17:24.000 --> 00:17:25.935
He's her go-to IT expert.

00:17:25.960 --> 00:17:27.856
ES: I seem to be technology-challenged

00:17:27.880 --> 00:17:31.416
and Darnell has come
to my rescue for over a decade.